body_html: Please provide details about what platform you are using (operating system, architecture). Also include your TensorFlow version. We ask for this in the issue submission template, because it is really difficult to help without that information. Thanks! My feeling is that DeepOSM has not updated for TensorFlow 1.0 yet and you are using TensorFlow 1.0, but that is speculation, since you didn't mention which versions.
